### apply agency
POST localhost:8080/agency/apply
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "name": "TOUR.U",
  "phone": "998999999999",
  "city": "Tashkent",
  "address": "Yunusobod",
  "email": "eurotouruz@eurotour.uz",
  "description": "tour to europe"
}

### approve agency
POST localhost:8080/agency/approve
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "agencyId": 2,
  "approve": true
}

### pending agencies
GET localhost:8080/agency/admin/pending-agencies
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### all agencies
GET localhost:8080/agency/all

